name: Swiftwick Aspire Four Running Socks - Unisex
description: These thin and lightweight running socks have minimal cushioning for comfort in close-fitting shoes without sacrificing sensitivity. The higher cuff protects ankles from trail and road debris.Durable nylon and olefin fabric manages moisture and breathability to keep your feet cool and comfortable.Firm support keeps feet going mile after mile.Midfoot arch band and y-heel keeps socks in place without bunching.Seamless toe for chafe-free comfort.Ultralight cushioning keeps feet comfortable without adding bulk.
